                - We reserve the right to review, modify, or remove posts that violate our guidelines, and unverified or misleading content may be marked or removed.
                <br>
                - Users are responsible for their uploads, and false claims or unethical behavior may lead to warnings or removal, with repeated violations resulting in account suspension or termination.
                <br>
                - Users can report content that appears inaccurate or harmful, and all reports will be reviewed.
                <br>
                - Do not post private or confidential information without consent, and handle personal data in accordance with applicable laws.
