                <br>
                These terms may change, and users will be notified of significant updates via the app; continued use indicates acceptance of any modifications.
                </p>
            </div>
    
            <p>&copy; 2024 Real. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Team: Curry Powder</p>
        </div>
    </footer>    
</body>

</html>